Package org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulators.tileentities

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BannerData
    Represents the information for a Banner such as the base color and BannerData.PatternLayers.
    BannerData.PatternLayer
    A representation on a single layer of a BannerData's pattern.
    BeaconData
    Represents the information for a Beacon.
    BrewingData
    Represents the information for a BrewingStand.
    CooldownData
    Represents the data of a Hopper that can be changed and applied.
    FurnaceData
    Represents the data for a Furnace.
    LockableData
    Represents a lock token for a TileEntity that can be locked.
    NoteData
    Represents data for a Note that defines what music can be played.
    SignData
    Represents the data for a Sign.
